Fins%2F20141114%2Fs00001%2F1415958948438SL4_52CB63A93D2DC47668B4F5731C836730.jpg&h=4106e6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20141114/s00001/1415958980761SL4_2BA9B26AA26E23C7C0F8A75DFD04834D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20141114%2Fs00001%2F1415958980761SL4_2BA9B26AA26E23C7C0F8A75DFD04834D.jpg&h=b37bb44a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20141114/s00001/1415959021883SL4_91A8D3C02B1F9D8F642058646C45E1FF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20141114%2Fs00001%2F1415959021883SL4_91A8D3C02B1F9D8F642058646C45E1FF.jpg&h=3c79b466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20141114/s00001/1415959086623SL4_E1CE99BD2EA1526064A8C1CE95B27B3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20141114%2Fs00001%2F1415959086623SL4_E1CE99BD2EA1526064A8C1CE95B27B3F.jpg&h=f2e26403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20141114/s00001/1415961762371SL4_20B67BB2C4ADD6F7B7FB5A319E0808A2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20141114%2Fs00001%2F1415961762371SL4_20B67BB2C4ADD6F7B7FB5A319E0808A2.jpg&h=758e4cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20141114/s00001/1415961783743SL4_70A9845ADE65BBA0F39FE10AEC5677C9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20141114%2Fs00001%2F1415961783743SL4_70A9845ADE65BBA0F39FE10AEC5677C9.jpg&h=8f05cb7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔領行動已經第40多天，近日盛傳警方清場在即，經歷過多次「胡椒噴霧對眼罩口罩」、「警棍對雨傘」的衝突後，旺角佔領者的防禦裝備不斷提升。<br />\n<br />\n佔領初期，示威者基本上只帶備口罩、眼罩、頭盔等。及後有人把膠墊捲成筒狀包裹雙手，同時綁上水樽等物品，亦有示威者帶備膠鉆板及浮板，作盾牌之用。<br />\n<br />\n城邦論學者、嶺南大學中文系助理教授陳雲，日前曾帶同一個由旅行箱改裝成的盾牌，到旺角佔領區向佔領者示範如何使用，他當時說，要拿起「篋盾」紥穩馬步，以抵擋清場行動。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲近日又透過社交網站轉載其他土法製作其他盾牌的過程，表示要「齊心造盾，保護城邦」，又透過社交網站轉載了一份木盾設計圖，圖中的木板主要由木板、兒童膠板、索帶、長縲絲、戒指等部件製造。設計者稱闊度與標準戰術盾相若，且備有穿手位，排除電鑽、鑽咀、士巴拿等工具後，每個成本約50至60元。<br />\n<br />\n（即時新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nCPPfqdr3x8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnCPPfqdr3x8&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9a41665a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nCPPfqdr3x8</a><br />\n<br />\n老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}